:INFO
Tin the Tip Before Every Session
Before soldering anything, apply a small amount of fresh solder to a clean iron tip. \
This is called tinning. Wipe the tip on a damp brass wool cleaner, apply a thin coat of \
solder, and wipe again. The tip should look bright and silver. A properly tinned

